01:43.926 --> 01:45.792
pay your creditors everything.

01:45.798 --> 01:46.813
What the...? But I thought

01:46.816 --> 01:48.812
bankruptcy was the cool law!

01:48.817 --> 01:50.353
The one that says "Dude, don't

01:50.356 --> 01:52.330
worry about it. I got this."

01:52.518 --> 01:53.370
Mr. Simpson,

01:53.557 --> 01:55.242
I'm afraid this court
must appoint

01:55.247 --> 01:57.161
