02:41.655 --> 02:43.403
that no one is interested in.

02:46.158 --> 02:48.201
I don't want to leave!

02:48.206 --> 02:50.461
You promised me I could die here!

02:50.465 --> 02:52.620
No, no. This place is too expensive.

02:52.636 --> 02:57.111
