03:12.795 --> 03:14.912
So... very...

03:27.665 --> 03:29.553
Scram, you two!

03:29.557 --> 03:31.282
This is my bedroom now!

03:31.286 --> 03:33.322
No way, this is our rec room!

03:33.325 --> 03:35.853
