05:58.596 --> 06:00.833
A sweet young thing like you?

06:00.835 --> 06:03.851
Wow, that's the first time anyone's ever

06:03.868 --> 06:06.561
put an adjective before calling me a thing.

06:17.135 --> 06:22.370
