06:22.445 --> 06:23.572
Hmm...

06:24.466 --> 06:26.690
Well, if he dies in my arms,

06:26.698 --> 06:28.833
I could meet a cute paramedic.

06:31.195 --> 06:33.731
All right, lips, man your kissing stations.

06:33.738 --> 06:35.132
This is not a drill.

06:40.757 --> 06:42.600
Well, here we are home early.

06:42.775 --> 06:45.963
Yeah, and the great prices at that new rib joint

06:45.965 --> 06:48.253
