07:00.907 --> 07:01.880
Do you?

07:01.965 --> 07:03.210
Yeah, I know who

07:03.216 --> 07:04.160
I was kissing,

07:04.168 --> 07:05.691
and I also know why.

07:05.696 --> 07:09.161
I'm a little shaky on when and where, but I got my theories.

07:09.167 --> 07:11.700
Well, I never, ever want to see that again.

07:11.804 --> 07:12.861
Ah, the hell with you.

07:12.863 --> 07:15.331
I just might ask that Selma girl out,

07:15.331 --> 07:17.479
and you can't tell me not to.

07:17.479 --> 07:19.543
My roof, my rules!

07:20.165 --> 07:22.921
Oh, why did I borrow that roof from him?

07:23.825 --> 07:27.731
So exactly what company am I giving these free boxes to?

07:27.736 --> 07:31.461
Uh... the name of the company is...

07:33.928 --> 07:34.501
Uh-huh.

07:34.698 --> 07:37.290
Are you run by dogs or for dogs?

07:37.296 --> 07:38.343
Actually, don't answer.

07:38.346 --> 07:39.771
I like not knowing.

07:40.565 --> 07:43.200
Now we just have to figure out what to do with these boxes.

07:43.206 --> 07:45.980
As always,I have some ideas.

07:46.576 --> 07:47.482
