08:02.386 --> 08:03.953
Well, actually,

08:03.955 --> 08:06.821
the real reason I asked you out is because I'm...

08:06.825 --> 08:08.773
well, I'm a little sweet on you.

08:08.778 --> 08:13.152
Oh, listen, Abe,the other night was fun, but...

08:13.157 --> 08:14.212
Ah, phooey on buts.

08:14.215 --> 08:16.333
At my age,and with your drawbacks,

08:16.348 --> 08:18.620
