It wasn't all frolicking.

09:34.206 --> 09:36.391
How could my Dad go out with Selma ?

09:36.655 --> 09:40.072
Don't those two gargoyles know that love
is for good-looking young people ?

09:40.395 --> 09:41.570
Well, gee, Homer, you, uh,

09:41.746 --> 09:44.353
ain't exactly open-casket
material yourself.

09:45.035 --> 09:46.463
Words hurt, you know.

09:48.886 --> 09:49.892
They do.

09:51.615 --> 09:53.861
Stupid Selma and Grampa.

09:54.078 --> 09:55.951
